Hultén, John Gunnar Ingvald, provinsialläkare, Vara, f. 24/2/92 i
translated:
Hultsjö, Jönköping. First marriage in 1919 to Ester Maria Larsson. Children: Lisa Carin born in 1919, Jan Gustaf Anders born in 1921. Studied: graduated high school in 1911, Bachelor of Medicine in 1915, Licentiate in Medicine in 1921 at Lund University. Second assistant physician at Linköping Hospital in 1917, acting physician in Sävsjö, and railway physician at the Lamhult-Sävsjö line in 1918. Acting medical examiner there from 1922, assistant physician at Sollefteå Hospital from 1921 to 1922, and physician at Biskopsbo mental hospital from 1922 to 1935. 

Hultén, John Gunnar Ingvald, provincial doctor, born on February 24, 1892, in Vara.
